				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">According to lucy:<br><br>By level 25 Renew Elements heals for 50pts.  It costs 25 mana to cast and thereby has a 2:1 ratio at and beyond level 25.<br><br>Renew Summoning, however, costs 100 mana and initially heals for 120 (at level 20) and finally heals up to 220 (at level 60).  Renew Summoning does not achieve a 2:1 ratio until level 50.<br><br>Conclusion:  Up until level 50 Renew Elements is more mana efficient than Renew Summoning.<br><br>P.S.<br>My only point on the weak nuke issue was that you may want to consider buying a white ceramic band so getting Burst of Flame takes up neither a slot nor mana.<br><br><br>Fenobleu Wayfarer<br>34th level Mage, Brell Serilis <p></p><i></i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
